<p><span class="anchor" id="p52"></span>بِالْمَبِيعِ<a href="#p52" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p53"></span>بعد زَوَال ملكه<a href="#p53" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
